      "span_text": "To further examine whether contact with VSG on living T. brucei is required for depletion of transitional B cells in vitro, T. brucei AnTat 1.1 trypanosomes were pre-incubated with a VSG-specific Nanobody (Nb, a dromedary heavy chain antibody fragment, devoid of its Fc part, having no detrimental effect on parasite survival  ), prior to addition to spleen cells from 5 day-infected mice."
